。全部法汉对照，所用例子均为基本会话的词汇，说明和建议浅显易懂。六位法藉人士参与录音，有男有女，还有两位儿童。兼顾自学者的需要，任何人都可循序渐进地学习法语法音。本书已在大学法语专业的初级班做过实验，效果良好。","price":"19.00元"},"book_id":"1108982","id":957905021},{"status":"wish","updated":"2015-09-15 17:36:25","user_id":"2274326","book":{"rating":{"max":10,"numRaters":1,"average":"0.0","min":0},"subtitle":"","author":["Stuckey, Barb"],"pubdate":"2013-3","tags":[{"count":1,"name":"烹饪","title":"烹饪"}],"origin_title":"","image":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s23003676.jpg","binding":"","translator":[],"catalog":"","pages":"368","images":{"small":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/spic\/s23003676.jpg","large":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/lpic\/s23003676.jpg","medium":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s23003676.jpg"},"alt":"https:\/\/book.douban.com\/subject\/11549021\/","id":"11549021","publisher":"","isbn10":"1439190747","isbn13":"9781439190746","title":"Taste","url":"http:\/\/api.douban.com\/v2\/book\/11549021","alt_title":"","author_intro":"","summary":"","price":"$ 18.08"},"book_id":"11549021","id":959277251},{"status":"read","comment":"好像啥都说了，又好像啥都没说……","updated":"2015-09-13 22:10:27","user_id":"2274326","rating":{"max":5,"value":"4","min":0},"book":{"rating":{"max":10,"numRaters":3632,"average":"9.3","min":0},"subtitle":"量子物理史话","author":["曹天元"],"pubdate":"2008-9","tags":[{"count":1670,"name":"科普","title":"科普"},{"count":1314,"name":"量子物理","title":"量子物理"},{"count":712,"name":"物理","title":"物理"},{"count":411,"name":"科学","title":"科学"},{"count":303,"name":"自然科学","title":"自然科学"},{"count":272,"name":"哲学","title":"哲学"},{"count":245,"name":"曹天元","title":"曹天元"},{"count":245,"name":"历史","title":"历史"}],"origin_title":"","image":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s3305272.jpg","binding":"平装","translator":[],"catalog":"第一章　黄金时代\n第二章　乌云\n第三章　火流星\n第四章　白云深处\n第五章　曙光\n第六章　殊途同归\n第七章　不确定性\n第八章　论战\n第九章　歧途\n第十章　回归经典\n第十一章　不等式的判决\n第十二章　新探险\n尾声\n外一篇　海森堡和德国原子弹计划\n后记","pages":"375","images":{"small":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/spic\/s3305272.jpg","large":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/lpic\/s3305272.